asset.title: Penny Skateboards X Bowl-A-Rama Bondi 2014
asset.description:
Penny Skateboards was back on the beaches of Bondi to celebrate the 10 year anniversary of Bowl-A-Rama. Penny came in full force with a Pop-Up shop and mini skate park where people were able to test out Penny boards, learn to skate, and see who could get the highest line on the Penny wall ride.  http://www.pennyskateboards.com

We had a great time with everyone who came to the event, and we're stoked to be part of such a great event put on by the Bowl-A-Rama crew.
